api-throttle-wait:
Taritari tae noa ki ngā hēkena $1 kua hipa. Kātahi, ka taea koe ki te tukua atu tāu tononga.

Aroha mai i te whakararu nei. Ko te kaupapa o te whakaroa te mahi whakapōturi ki te tahotaho ngā rawa o ngā tūmau.

Panui i $2 ki te whakamōhio i ngā mokamoka ki a koe.

faq-old-data-title: He aha ahau i kore ai e taea te kite ngā raraunga kei te tawhito i $1?
faq-old-data-body: I te tau 2015 i a Here-turi-kōkā, ka tū te API pageviews nō Wikimedia. I whakakī ki te API i ngā raraunga i $1. Mehemea kei te pīrangi koe ki te kimi ngā raraunga i ngā wā i mua $1, me whakamahitia tētahi atu taputapu. Ko stats.grok.se tētahi taputapu pai hei kimi ngā raraunga o mua. Ki te hē tētahi atu taputapu, kāhore me ui koe ki ngā kaitiaki o te taputapu nei.
faq-todays-date-title: He aha ahua i kore ai e taea te kite ngā raraunga nō tēnei rā?
faq-todays-date-body: I te nuinga o te wā, 24 hāora te wā whakakī ki te API i ngā raraunga hou.  I ētahi wā, ka ngaro ngā raraunga nō inanahi.  Mehemea ka ngaro ngā raraunga nā, ka murua te whakamātakitaki; kāhore ka whakaatuhia tētahi kore.
faq-agents-user: tāngata katoa e titiro ana i he whārangi ipurangi; Ko ngā kaitātari, rātou ko ngā kaitātari muna, ko te tāngata e pānui ana.
faq-agents-spider: ngā kaiwhakaputunga nā ngā initia kimi (whakatauira: Kūkara) e tukua mai ana i ngā whārangi hei whakapai i ngā mahi kimi. I ētahi wā, he maha ngā titiro nā ngā kaiwhakaputunga; ko tēnei te kaupapa e whakaatu ana te pūmanawa i ngā titiro nā ngā tāngata anake.
faq-agents-bot: ētahi atu pūmanawa aunoa e tukua mai ana ngā whārangi hei kaupapa ngaro.
faq-chart-type-title: He aha te ara ki te whakarerekē te momo tūtohi.
faq-chart-type-body: Pāwhiria "$1" ki te kōwhiringia tētahi o ngā momo e ono.  Ka tiaki te pūmanawa tautono i tāu kōwhiringa.  I ngā wā noa, i a koe e mātaki ana i kotahi whārangi, ka whakaatu te pūmanawa tautono i te tūtohi tapawhā; i a koe e mātaki ana i ētahi whārangi, ka whakaatu i te tūtohi raina.  I a koe e whakamahi ana i te tūtohi takakau, te tūtohi porotaka i roto, me te tūtohi koki roto rite, me kōwhiritia ngā rā.
faq-top-viewed-title: Kei te pirangi ahau ki ngā whārangi ipurangi e titiro rawa atu ana i ētahi rā.
faq-multi-lang-title: Kei te pīrangi ahau ki te kimi i te raraunga mō kotahi whārangi ipurangi ki te reo katoa.
faq-try-tool: Ka taea e koe te kite tēnei ki $1.
faq-bug-report-title: He tono tāku, he take tāku rainei hei pūrongorongo ki ngā kaitiaki.
faq-bug-report-body: Mehemea kei te pīrangi koe ki te whakamahi tētahi "wiki" ki te kōrero ki ngā kaitiaki hei whakamātau i āu whakaaro, ka whakamahitia tēnei ki te "Wiki Meta". E taea hoki e koe te rīpoata ngā taki ki a GitHub rānei, ki a Phabricator rānei.
faq-topviews-false-positive-title: He aha ō ētahi whārangi titiro e tino maha nā?
faq-topviews-false-positive-body1: He nama manakore ēna. Ahakoa he whakapōrearea ngā nama manakore, kāhore e taea te whakakore ēna. Ko tētahi whakatauira, ka mahi tētahi pūmanawa rorohiko aunoa ki te tukua atu tētahi whārangi i ngā wā katoa. Ko tētahi rautaki ki te rapuhia ngā nama manakore te mahi whakataurite: ka whakataurite ngā titiro o ngā rorohiko papa mahi ki te titiro o ngā waea pūkoro. I te nuinga o ngā wā, he nui ngā titiro o ngā waea pūkoro i ngā titiro o ngā rorohiko papa mahi. Mehemea he iti ngā titiro o ngā waea pūkoro, he nama manakore, pea.
faq-topviews-false-positive-body2: Ka taea e koe te kite te tātari tētahi whārangi.  Mehema kei te pīrangi koe, pāwhiria te kaute titiro ki te taha matau.  He tika te raraunga kei konā.  Mehemea he keokeo pūrei i roto i ngā kaute titiro, ka taea pea te whakamarama e ngā ropu ko Wikimedia Analytics.
faq-source-pageviews: - te tepeka o ngā titiro e tangohia mai ana e te whakakaupapa
faq-source-unique-devices: - te tapeke o ngā rorohiko e tuku ana te wahi ipurangi
faq-massviews-sources-pagepile: ko te nama o tētahi kāhui whārangi e hangaia ana ki $1.  Ka taea e koe te hanga ngā ripanga, ka tukua atu ēna ki te taputapu ko Massviews, ki te tātaritia ō ēna whārangi titiro.
faq-massviews-sources-category: ko te katoa o te hononga o tētahi whārangi momo (whakatuaira: $1)
faq-massviews-sources-template: ko te katoa o te URL o tētahi whārangi tauira (whakatauira: $1). Ko te kāhui hua ngā whārangi e mahi ana i te tauira.
faq-massviews-sources-quarry: ko te nama me te whakakaupapa o ngā raraunga $1.  Ko $2 ō ngā whārangi ingoa.
faq-massviews-subject-page-body: I a koe e whakamahi ana i tētahi momo whārangi hei ūkaipō, ka taea e koe te whakamahi tēnei kōwhiringa. I ētahi wā, kei roto ngā whārangi kōrero i te momo whārangi, engari kei te pīrangi koe ki ngā whārangi kaupapa. Ko tētahi whakatauira e rārangi ana i ngā whārangi kōrero : FA-Class New York City articles
faq-throttle-wait-title: Me tatari ahua tae noa ki te hipa ngā hēkena $1. He aha te take?
faq-throttle-wait-body: Ka taea e te API Pageviews nō Wikimedia te whakahoki ngā tononga iti i ia wā.  E whakamahi ana te pūmanawa i te takaroa $1 ngā hēkena hei karo i te whakapaunga tūmau.
url-structure-example:
Mehemea kei te pīrangi koe ki te whakamahi ngā kōwhiringa noa hei tuku mai i te raraunga hou nō tētahi whārangi i tētahi "wiki", whakamahitia:
$1
Me whakakapi tētahi $3 whaimana i $2.  Ka whakarerekētia te $4 ki te whārangi e kawe ana i te hononga.
url-structure-example-siteviews:
Mehemea kei te pīrangi koe ki te whakamahitia ngā kōwhiringa noa hei tuku mai i te kaute o ngā titiro katoa nō ngā whārangi katoa i tētahi "wiki", whakamahitia:
$1
url-structure-topviews-example:
Mehemea kei te pīrangi koe ki te kite te raupapa o ngā whārangi e titiro rawa ana i tētahi "wiki", whakamahitia:
$1
Me whakakapi tētahi $3 whaimana i $2.  Ka taea e koe te whakamahi te $4 ki te whakakore ētahi whārangi.
url-structure-parameters-order: Ka taea te whakamahi ngā taurangi i ia raupapa, i ia raupapa.
url-structure-project: Ko $1, tērā atu whakakaupapa whaimana rānei ($2)

url-structure-excludes: Ko ētahi ingoa whārangi ipurangi e unuhia ana, e rikorikotia ana, e wehe ana ki ngā tohu kōrere (|). Ko ēnei whārangi ngā whārangi whakapōrearea, ngā whārangi manakore ki a koe. (Ko tētahi whakatauira: Main_page|Special:Search)
url-structure-onwiki-link: E whakamahitia ana $1 ki te hono tētahi whārangi ipurangi i tētahi wiki ki konei.

url-structure-start-date: Ko te rā timitanga e whakatakotohia ana pēnei ki $1; mehema ka ngaro te kōwhiringa nei me te kōwhiringa ko $2, ka tukua mai te raraunga hou
url-structure-end-date: Ko te rā whakamutunga e whakatakotohia ana pēnei ki $1; i ngā wā noa, ko $1 te rā
url-structure-agent: Ko tētahi o $1(ngā tāngata; ko tēnei te noa), $2 (kaiwhakaputunga o ngā initia kimi), $3 (kaiwhakaputunga o te Wikimedia Foundation), $4 (te katoa)

url-structure-sort-direction: Te ahu o te whakaraupapa.  Ko $1 te whakaraupapa iho. Ko $2 te whaharaupapa ake.
